{"tid":330148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史上第二位　印度將選出「賤民」總統","createTime":"2017-07-21T02:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T12:29:48.000Z","uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba6d4ce0390bdce113b8cf7d5dc9aef13751c53","tid":330148,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"史上第二位　印度將選出「賤民」總統 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170717/640_747f201d36ac53e442d7827b0498109a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170717%2F640_747f201d36ac53e442d7827b0498109a.jpg&h=a767e8e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度立法議員今天展開總統選舉投票，預料將選出前律師、前比哈省總督科文德（Ram Nath Kovind）作為新總統。他也將成為該國歷史上，第二位來自最低社會階層「賤民」（Dalit）的總統。印度史上首位賤民總統是1997-2002年出任第10任總統的納瑞雅南(KR Narayanan)。印度總統為「虛位元首」，實際掌權者為總理莫迪（Narendra Modi），全國超過4900名立法議員已經開始投票，將於本周四宣布結果。 <br />\n法新社報導，71歲的科文德資歷完整，隸屬總理莫迪的右翼政黨「印度人民黨」（BJP），一旦他當選為總統，將進一步鞏固莫迪的權力，並對「賤民」階級釋放正面訊息。 <br />\n<br />\n在印度的種姓制度中，「賤民」是地位最低下的階層，生活最貧困且遭到邊緣化。在該國13億人口中，有2億為「賤民」。儘管印度以現代法律試圖保護賤民，但賤民仍飽受歧視，時常無法獲得教育及工作晉升機會。 <br />\n<br />\n巧合的是，科文德的主要競爭對手、隸屬最大反對黨聯盟團結進步聯盟（UPA）的女政治人物庫瑪（Meira Kumar），同樣來自「賤民」階級。庫瑪為前國會下議院院長。（林奐成／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170717/1162906/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170717%2F1162906%2F&d=R2uFPyzZ62JHJP0JLPRnzNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=f27143e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170717/1162906/</a>"},{"pid":"9685511c3d3e626ad3a76cd31baebe75531d2736","tid":330148,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/104605_07b6a65bea229d908eb61027d7fd3fc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F104605_07b6a65bea229d908eb61027d7fd3fc8.jpg&h=4c0bd86d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315ab290c87679a125a5037292a6ffb930215abb","tid":330148,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:36:45.000Z","msg":"印度都有進步<br />\n支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec887756167086501f24d39178a271a491e365ba","tid":330148,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"實際掌權者為總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e11770b0ee99dfe43b8337f0b83b90e561c175","tid":330148,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>實際掌權者為總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nplease Google keywords:議會制"},{"pid":"2008cc22d8885de8cd710016fef298bbf8483104","tid":330148,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>實際掌權者為總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ccc62b445ac568e574715cf9a070ba2630dd25","tid":330148,"uid":36421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:29:48.000Z","msg":"同德國總統一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}